Function Controls

● COMMAND DIAL LOCK ● AF-ON
● ZOOM/FOCUS CONTROL RING ● AWB LOCK ONLY
● CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (T) ● LOCK SETTING
● CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (W) ● PERFORMANCE
● MF CONSTANT SPEED FOCUS (N) ● AUTO IMAGE TRANSFER ORDER
● MF CONSTANT SPEED FOCUS (F) ● Bluetooth ON/OFF
● AE LOCK ONLY ● QUICK MENU
● AF LOCK ONLY ● PLAYBACK
● AE/AF LOCK ● NONE

To disable the function button, choose NONE.
Selected function lock is not available when CONSTANT SPEED
ZOOM (T) or CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (W) is assigned to a lens
function button (目 300).
